Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:02.75,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{Time shift -5}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:04.31,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even fate can be used as a hint for reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:06.06,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing through the most mysterious cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:07.86,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's stage is Nanki-Shirahama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.11,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The footprints of crime on a white sandy beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.57,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:13.57,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:15.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:47.54,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{Timeshift -369}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.54,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shirahama Station\NJR Kinokuni Line
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! Let's go check out souvenirs at the waiting room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have to go look for souvenirs just yet, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, look! It's Mr. Sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No surprise finding this in the plum-producing Kishu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's buy some on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so cute about a sour-looking guy like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nambo Kumakusunoki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's read Minakata Kumagusu Kinenkan—\NMinakata Kumagusu Memorial Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a world-famous botanist who was born in Wakayama Prefecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,especially known for his research of plants and fungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, they had a great researcher like that here, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'd advise you to study a bit before travelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop by for a meal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crawfish here is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still a bit early...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check out the memorial hall first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.80,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Minakata Kumagusu Memorial Hall Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The road's closed on this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:42.57,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Minakata Kumagusu Memorial Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:04.09,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shirarahama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, the sand is really fine and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why it's so white.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I once heard that the secret of its whiteness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is that it's quartz sand consisting to 90% of silicate acid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. He sure knows a lot of trivia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to take this sand home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, put it into a little bottle and carry it around with me, like you do with star sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you go again with your girlish tastes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were looking at a weird keychain back at the station too, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One with umeboshi attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You moron! Only brats like things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but aren't you Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! I'm a fan of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I take your picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wow! What a knockout!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the famous detective you all know, Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, could you take a picture of the two of us together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you come here to investigate a case or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah. We're just sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won a raffle at the shopping center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all students?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're seniors at Naniwa Medical University.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're doctors in the making!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce everyone, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girl next to you is the queen of our group, Maki Shinjo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:53.04,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Maki Shinjo (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, cut it out, Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next to her is our gigolo, Tatsuhiko Yura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:56.00,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiko Yura (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our Madonna, Madoka Mitsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.46,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Madoka Mitsui (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's our whiz kid, Kanako Miyahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.92,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kanako Miyahara (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.76,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kota Fuji (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm the clown of the group, Kota Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three of them are in the art club,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and since Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} suggested we take a nature-sketching trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we all decided to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though it's more like we're here to help Miss Rich Lady pass the time.{kanemochi o-jou-san}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about grateful, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She paid for the hotel, train tickets, and the rental car fee as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yura! You've got no class, talking like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I broke up with her because I didn't like just what she's doing for all of us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, she spends hundreds of thousands of yen every month just on cosmetics...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time a new product goes on the market, she has it sent in from Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Madoka has no money, just like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and doesn't look down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her childishness is a fly in the ointment though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you lucky, finding yourself a cutie-pie to go out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't bother me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanako, can you go get me something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go get it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to be at your beck and call anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that thanks to you teaching me math,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which wasn't my strong point, during high-school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made it into university.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do appreciate what you did for me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But would you stop bossing me around, harping on how grateful I should be to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to boss you around...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we've all come on this trip together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so why don't we all just go on and have a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go get the drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll have Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} do things for me instead of Kanako from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it was that fainted during practical dissection practice, and was saved by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You promised you'd keep that a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be right back, so wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what are your plans for after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to Shirahama Energy Land right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go to the underwater observatory
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Sandambeki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before finally watching the sunset from Senjojiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the morning, we're thinking of going to Adventure World...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come along with us, Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks, we've already got plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, where are you staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the Shin'yuzaki Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, we'd better get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, have a nice trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those people, you can't tell if they're getting along or not, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, when you're young, anything goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:19.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sandambeki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really a bold sheer cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like you can go all the way to over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, why don't we go tour the caves, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we can go down by elevator from that building over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after that, we get to watch the sunset at Senjojiki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll be super-beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:45.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Senjojiki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a magnificent view!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure glad we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was worth coming, just to see this sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you come to watch the sunset too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:09:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I've never seen the sunset from here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you like sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, why not stop over at the Tore Tore Market before going to Adventure World tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tore Tore Market?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from fresh seafood,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they have a whole line of top-quality locally-brewed sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you say locally-brewed sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can send it home by courier service too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've also written the bus route to the market from Shin'yuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a bus stop called Bus Depot{...seriously? - Yep. Garage or car shed work too. XD} near the Tore Tore Market.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any buses that go directly from Tore Tore Market to Adventure World,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so you'll have to get off once at Shirahama Station, but it shouldn't take that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for all your kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll visit there for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for all your thoughtfulness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came all the way here just to tell us about the market, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess she's just a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:15.07,Character Card,,0,0,0,,The next day\NRuins of Marine Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.41,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shirarahama
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.33,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sandambeki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.25,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Adventure World
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.22,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tore Tore Market
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bus for Adventure World is the #3.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next bus to Adventure World is at 10:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means we've got 20 minutes left to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we take a stroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt like someone was watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was probably just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want it so badly, why don't you buy it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go take a look in the souvenir shop outside too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:42.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we've only got 7 or 8 minutes left, so we'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, would you mind if I stop over at the store of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have time, you know. Hurry it up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So you're going to buy it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone's watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up! The bus is gonna leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only one left?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:18.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone other than Ran bought one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, that bus is headed for Sandambeki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.85,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Adventure World
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, wave, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's only a kid, and yet he's embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, it's you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd run into you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuji! Kota Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everyone else here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Three of them went out to sketch in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said she was going to go for a drive until sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw her around 10:00 at Shirahama Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there! Let's go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a laptop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you always carry it around with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Yura calls me a computer freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down and tell me again, Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, this is Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is she and what happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.49,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the bushes at Sandambeki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.49,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's a knife in her chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sandambeki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That suspicious person was on the bus to Sandambeki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're all headed your way. Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called the police already, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about Yura and Kanako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it, I'll get in touch with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't we just pass the entrance to Sandambeki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is further inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Over there in the bushes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A knife stab through the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably died on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wallet is nowhere in sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However you look at it, this seems to be a robbery-murder case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There are no signs of a struggle nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's a good chance the killer was an acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I recall correctly, Maki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s keychain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...had the rental car key on it too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Does that mean the killer took it and fled in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But this key chain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:23.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Work gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why does she have work gloves on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't I told you time and time again not to mess around at crime scenes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's wait for the police to come before we investigate any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow! Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:44.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:45.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am O'ura from the Wakayama Prefectural Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Ando, from the Shirahama East Police Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am honored to be able to work with you,\Nthe great detective Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:17.11,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Detective Ando (29)\NShirahama East\NPolice Station Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:17.11,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Detective O'ura (35)\NWakayama Prefectural\NPolice Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do give us precise advice if need be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, cooperating with the police is the duty of any citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help in whatever way I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let me introduce you to the friends of the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kota Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who rushed over here with us from Adventure World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kanako Miyahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who came over here from Engetsu Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Madoka Mitsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who first found the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is Tatsuhiko Yura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who came here from Shirarahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Madoka Mitsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,please tell us the circumstances under which you found Maki Shinjo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard Beethoven playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beethoven?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sketching on the far end of Sandambeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I heard a cell phone ringtone playing from behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I went toward the bushes, where the sound was coming from...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I called Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the place where Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was lying was fairly close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, you didn't notice that a crime was being committed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was facing the other way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the sound of the waves was rather loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you heard the cell phone's ringtone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Electronic sounds like those of cell phones are made to be audible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Ando, please give us a report on the autopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:19:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is shock by a stab wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no sign of the corpse having been moved after death,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the estimated time of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in other words, the time the murder is thought to have been committed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,judging by the condition of the body, is between 9 and 11 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the time of the murder can be narrowed down a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at Shirahama Station at about ten minutes after 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was about 10:10?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After bowing to us, she left immediately in her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were going to get on the 10:15 bus headed for Adventure World,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'm sure about the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Ando.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long does it take to get from Shirahama Station to Sandambeki by car?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's tour season now, it should take less than 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's say it takes about 14 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she arrives at Sandambeki about 10:24.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she parks the car in the alley closest to the scene of the crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would take her 2 minutes to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we assume she was killed immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the time the murder was committed would be around 10:26 at the earliest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can narrow it down to the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ca. 34 minutes between 10:26 and 11:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wallet seems to have disappeared from among her personal effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a few minutes ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the car that the victim was thought to have been driving
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was found near Sansho Shrine, about 3 km away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An empty wallet was found inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Maki's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we've already gotten to the bottom of this case. This case is—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the key of the car found?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the key was in the car's ignition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you only receive one key from the car rental shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think they usually give you two keys, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a robbery-murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After attacking Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the killer stole the car and fled in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then abandoned it near Sansho Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:06.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No. It's probably just made to look like a robbery-murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:10.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's most likely that this murder was committed by an acquaintance of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:11.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:14.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the killer is among us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so in order to contain the secret you decided to shut her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanki-Shirahama...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer must be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:15.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Cosmetics
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:23.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, the solution! Figured out who did it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:24.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It has to be the person who bought Mr. Sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:25.61,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That would be {\i1}you{\i0}!
